title._content: Clearing a fireline in McDonald Forest

description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC1008 Image Description: Horses are being used to clear a major fireline along a ridge in McDonald Forest. Snags were felled and burned with trash and down logs. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
